  <source>Watson Pharmaceuticals</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study explores the safety and efficacy of intravenous iron therapy in anemic
      hemodialysis patients treated with epoetin alfa, who have higher serum ferritin levels, but
      low to normal transferrin saturation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
